---
<div id="mobile-why-choose-us" style="width: 480px; background-color: #ffffff; padding: 40px 0; box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;">
  
  <!-- Left column texts moved to the top -->
  <div style="width: 450px; padding: 0 15px; box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 35px;">
    <!-- Title -->
    <h2 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 30px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.1em; color: #111111; margin: 0 0 8px 0;">
      Thinking About<br>Building an ADU?
    </h2>
    
    <!-- Subtitle -->
    <p style="font-family: Inter, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.1em; color: #444444; margin: 0 0 25px 0;">
      You're Right to Be Careful.
    </p>
    
    <!-- Paragraphs -->
    <p style="font-family: Inter, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.2em; color: #007BC3; margin: 0 0 12px 0;">
      Let's be honest:
    </p>
    
    <p style="font-family: Inter, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.2em; color: #7E7E7E; margin: 0 0 16px 0;">
      The construction industry has a reputation problem. Between confusing city zoning laws, contractors who disappear mid-project, and quotes that balloon after the concrete is poured, it's no surprise homeowners hesitate.
    </p>
    
    <p style="font-family: Inter, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.2em; color: #7E7E7E; margin: 0 0 16px 0;">
      An ADU is a $150,000+ investment. You deserve a contractor who treats your home with respect and your budget with transparency.
    </p>
    
    <p style="font-family: Inter, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.2em; color: #7E7E7E; margin: 0;">
      That's why every project with MY Home Builders starts with a fixed, written scope before we break ground, a dedicated project manager from day one, and a team that's licensed, bonded, and insured. Not a subcontractor roulette.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Icon boxes stacked below -->
  <div style="width: 450px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 24px; box-sizing: border-box;">
    
    <!-- Box 1: Fully Licensed & Insured -->
    <div style="display: flex; gap: 15px; align-items: flex-start; padding: 0 15px; box-sizing: border-box; width: 100%;">
      <!-- Icon -->
      <img alt="Fully Licensed" src="/images/fully-licensed.png" style="width: 50px; height: auto; flex-shrink: 0;" />
      <!-- Content -->
      <div style="flex-grow: 1;">
        <!-- Blue bar title -->
        <div style="background-color: #0071c8; padding: 8px 12px; box-sizing: border-box; width: 100%; margin-bottom: 6px;">
          <h4 style="color: #ffffff; font-family: Inter, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; margin: 0; text-transform: uppercase;">
            Fully Licensed & Insured
          </h4>
        </div>
        <!-- Description -->
        <p style="color: #7E7E7E; font-family: Inter, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2em; margin: 0;">
          CA Lic. #1002927. Your property is protected from day one.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Box 2: Iron-Clad Fixed Pricing -->
    <div style="display: flex; gap: 15px; align-items: flex-start; padding: 0 15px; box-sizing: border-box; width: 100%;">
      <!-- Icon -->
      <img alt="Fixed Pricing" src="/images/fixed-pricing.png" style="width: 50px; height: auto; flex-shrink: 0;" />
      <!-- Content -->
      <div style="flex-grow: 1;">
        <!-- Blue bar title -->
        <div style="background-color: #0071c8; padding: 8px 12px; box-sizing: border-box; width: 100%; margin-bottom: 6px;">
          <h4 style="color: #ffffff; font-family: Inter, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; margin: 0; text-transform: uppercase;">
            Iron-Clad Fixed Pricing
          </h4>
        </div>
        <!-- Description -->
        <p style="color: #7E7E7E; font-family: Inter, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2em; margin: 0;">
          Written scope of work before we break ground. No surprise change orders.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Box 3: Dedicated Project Manager -->
    <div style="display: flex; gap: 15px; align-items: flex-start; padding: 0 15px; box-sizing: border-box; width: 100%;">
      <!-- Icon -->
      <img alt="Project Manager" src="/images/project-manager.png" style="width: 50px; height: auto; flex-shrink: 0;" />
      <!-- Content -->
      <div style="flex-grow: 1;">
        <!-- Blue bar title -->
        <div style="background-color: #0071c8; padding: 8px 12px; box-sizing: border-box; width: 100%; margin-bottom: 6px;">
          <h4 style="color: #ffffff; font-family: Inter, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; margin: 0; text-transform: uppercase;">
            Dedicated Project Manager
          </h4>
        </div>
        <!-- Description -->
        <p style="color: #7E7E7E; font-family: Inter, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.2em; margin: 0;">
          One point of contact. No chasing people down for updates.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>
